    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of buckthorn shrub indigenous to China; its bark was used to extract a green dye used on wool and silk. It is grown in Europe as an ornamental plant.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
